				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Just an addendum of the input latency question, since you asked. As far as the GB CPU is concerned, it's instant. On a SGB it is, of course, dependent on the SNES CPU. Data will only arrive at the SGB CPU when the SNES CPU propagates it to the cartridge, through the controller chip, however that works exactly from the SNES side.</div>

